</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488000' id='t-488000'>Put all these three together, and you have a nice little map</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='490000' id='t-490000'>of the entire boundary of visual iconography</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='493000' id='t-493000'>which comics can embrace.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='495000' id='t-495000'>And if you move to the right you also get language,</span>
