<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611000' id='t-611000'>And it was just a little thing -- it wasn't good for much except text entry --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614000' id='t-614000'>but my father had told me about Moore's Law,</span>
