<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>as the content of the new technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='653000' id='t-653000'>And so, what they would do is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654000' id='t-654000'>they'd have these comic pages that resemble print comics pages,</span>
