<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660000' id='t-660000'>The problem was, that if you go with this idea --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662000' id='t-662000'>this basic idea that space equals time in comics --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>what happens is that when you introduce sound and motion,</span>
