<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677000' id='t-677000'>Interactivity was another thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678000' id='t-678000'>There were hypertext comics.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679000' id='t-679000'>But the thing about hypertext</span>
