<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='683000' id='t-683000'>it's profoundly non-spatial.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>The distance from Abraham Lincoln to a Lincoln penny,</span>
