<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>to &quot;Plan 9&quot; to nine lives:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691000' id='t-691000'>it's all the same.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693000' id='t-693000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694000' id='t-694000'>And -- but in comics, in comics,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>every aspect of the work, every element of the work</span>
