<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703000' id='t-703000'>So the question was:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>was there any way to preserve that spatial relationship</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707000' id='t-707000'>while still taking advantage of all of the things</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709000' id='t-709000'>that digital had to offer us?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711000' id='t-711000'>And I found my personal answer for this</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713000' id='t-713000'>in those ancient comics that I was showing you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716000' id='t-716000'>Each of them has a single unbroken reading line,</span>
