<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>that as you move through space you move through time</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733000' id='t-733000'>is being carried out without any compromise,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='735000' id='t-735000'>but there were compromises when print hit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738000' id='t-738000'>Adjacent spaces were no longer adjacent moments,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='741000' id='t-741000'>so the basic idea of comics was being broken again and again</span>
